#
# This systemd unit is retained in-place (D-18) until the VPS cutover is
# confirmed successful. Once Docker Compose has been running cleanly in
# production for a verification window, this file (plus docker-compose.dev.yml
# removal and any remaining deprecated-in-place references) will be removed
# in a follow-up cleanup phase.
#
# Cutover runbook:
#   .planning/phases/999.2-devdock-self-containerization/999.2-HUMAN-UAT.md
#
# Cutover commands (summary):
#   sudo systemctl stop devdock
#   sudo systemctl disable devdock
#   # (update host nginx configs per deploy/nginx/*.conf changes)
#   sudo nginx -t && sudo systemctl reload nginx
#   cd /home/murx-dev/devdock && docker compose up -d --build
